        <section id="section_bb1_krh_wcb">
            <title>Audit Rotation</title>
            <p>The auditing Rotation parameters can be only one of the following:</p>
            <p>
                <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_l34_nrh_wcb">
